<subSubSection id="5144197D9FA87EBC4F1217DC71546E62" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" type="taxon discussion">
<paragraph id="79D1D19965BBF89465CF8A1AA4451E05" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">Taxon discussion</paragraph>
<paragraph id="277D240BF08975463D7DA7D0B1CB5075" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">
Scattered in the mountains of north and central Greece, 
<taxonomicName id="B17D12AD4706C2D797B7426F2AB71AF5" class="Liliopsida" family="Asphodelaceae" genus="Asphodeline" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Asphodeline taurica" order="Asparagales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="taurica">
<emphasis id="ABB2166A74BB81B51EDE376DCD99F831" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">Asphodeline taurica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
reaches Sterea Ellas and north Peloponnisos to the south, with its southernmost Greek locality on Mt. Chelmos (
<bibRefCitation id="E4082E7F0CD04C8C711EB75D43260CD5" author="Goulimis, C. N." journalOrPublisher="Athens" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7668186" refString="Goulimis, C. N., 1960. New additions to the Greek flora. Second series. Athens" title="New additions to the Greek flora. Second series" year="1960">Goulimis 1960</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="E0F700E14511D7D78906572D9B1C8A1F" author="Andersson, I. A." journalOrPublisher="Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7667728" refString="Andersson, I. A., 1991. Mountain Flora of Greece 2. Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" title="Mountain Flora of Greece 2" year="1991">Andersson 1991b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="4123039CB799B7DE4FCB9513F7FE3E72" author="Authier, P." journalOrPublisher="Candollea" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" pagination="483 - 497" refId="B7667776" refString="Authier, P., 1994. Contributions a &quot;Flora Hellenica&quot;: la flore de la region des Monts Timfi (Parc national du Vikos-Aoos, Epire, nord-ouest Grece) (II). Candollea 49: 483 - 497" title="Contributions a &quot; Flora Hellenica &quot;: la flore de la region des Monts Timfi (Parc national du Vikos-Aoos, Epire, nord-ouest Grece) (II)" volume="49" year="1994">Authier 1994</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="F73D95BAE33B32C03A0F710FD0B2F0BB" author="Authier, P." journalOrPublisher="Candollea" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" pagination="209 - 244" refId="B7667785" refString="Authier, P., 2002. Catalogue commente de la flore de la region des monts Timfi (parc national du Vikos-Aoos et environs - Epire - Nord-ouest Grece). 7. Liliaceae. Candollea 56: 209 - 244" title="Catalogue commente de la flore de la region des monts Timfi (parc national du Vikos-Aoos et environs - Epire - Nord-ouest Grece). 7. Liliaceae" volume="56" year="2002">Authier 2002</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="C2ABE93C15B987A2D9231A6DB0655CF8" author="Tan, K." journalOrPublisher="Phytologia Balcanica, 12 (2): 279 - 301" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7669649" refString="Tan, K., Vold, G., Sfikas, G., 2006. New floristic records in the Balkans: 2. Phytologia Balcanica, 12 (2): 279-301" title="New floristic records in the Balkans: 2" year="2006">Tan et al. 2006</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EE2F7A15307B82D72D87BD8FC8F25674" author="Strid, A." journalOrPublisher="Society for the Protection of Prespa, Agios Germanos, Prespa" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7669537" refString="Strid, A., Bermeier, E., Fotiadis, G., 2020. Flora and Vegetation of the Prespa National Park, Greece. Society for the Protection of Prespa, Agios Germanos, Prespa" title="Flora and Vegetation of the Prespa National Park, Greece" year="2020">Strid et al. 2020</bibRefCitation>
; herbarium specimens preserved in B with JACQ-IDs 655330 and 655358). In the floristic region of NE Greece, the species has been reported from Mt. Falakro (
<bibRefCitation id="7D0D12D10F80CED745BB7E29F2BFCAE7" author="Tan, K." journalOrPublisher="Phytologia Balcanica, 12 (2): 279 - 301" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7669649" refString="Tan, K., Vold, G., Sfikas, G., 2006. New floristic records in the Balkans: 2. Phytologia Balcanica, 12 (2): 279-301" title="New floristic records in the Balkans: 2" year="2006">Tan et al. 2006</bibRefCitation>
), Mt. Papikio (
<bibRefCitation id="DF699C4CF4995665BD5108023C4B8884" author="Andersson, I. A." journalOrPublisher="Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7667728" refString="Andersson, I. A., 1991. Mountain Flora of Greece 2. Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" title="Mountain Flora of Greece 2" year="1991">Andersson 1991b</bibRefCitation>
) and Mt. Angistro (JACQ-ID 655358, B!). Our records (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="CEF9792BBB5561BE7C76977C7205125E" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F7677551" captionText="Figure 4. Asphodeline taurica from Mt. Pangeo (photo: K. Goula)." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e81817.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/640523" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">4</figureCitation>
) add three new mountains to the distribution of this species, uncommon in Greece.
</paragraph>
